parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy properly or may deploy unnecessarily.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the airbag deploys with excessive force
or the airbag causes injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The recall of Takata airbags has led to a shortage of replacement parts, causing delays and inconvenience to vehicle owners, and potentially putting them at risk of injury or death due to defective airbags.
symptoms: Delayed or unavailable replacement parts
lack of communication from dealers or manufacturers
and uncertainty about the safety of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which may lead to a failure to deploy or an unexpected deployment, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission shifter can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The gear shift lever is stuck in park
the vehicle will not shift out of park
the gear shift lever is difficult to move
the vehicle is stuck in neutral.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and jerking can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The transmission slips and jerks
the vehicle loses power
the vehicle hesitates when shifting gears
the transmission makes a grinding or whining noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The engine stalls
the vehicle loses power
the engine makes a loud noise
the engine warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag and electrical issues can cause the vehicle's safety features to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The airbag light is illuminated
the seat belt does not function properly
the electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
hesitates to start
or experiences intermittent power loss; warning lights on the dashboard illuminate; flickering or complete failure of headlights
interior lights
and other electrical components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle control can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates unexpectedly; the throttle pedal sticks or feels soft; the vehicle hesitates to accelerate; warning lights on the dashboard illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls; the fuel gauge is inaccurate; fuel leaks; warning lights on the dashboard illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates to shift gears; the transmission slips or jerks; warning lights on the dashboard illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the BCM can cause various electrical components to malfunction, leading to accidents or distractions while driving.
symptoms: The headlights
interior lights
and other electrical components flicker or fail; warning lights on the dashboard illuminate; the vehicle's computer system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy in the event of a crash, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates; the airbags deploy unexpectedly; the airbags fail to deploy in a crash.
